stently checked for optimum cooling temperatures and all our staff are fully trained in identifying good and bad meat.<\/p>"}},"question_8gzLgT":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Is your meat halal?","text":"<p>All our meat is prepared and prescribed in accordance with Islamic law.<\/p>"}},"question_JjTrRU":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Where should you go to buy fresh meat?","text":"<p>Reputable butchers are the best source for fresh meat. As experts in the trade, we are best able to identify the good from the bad. At MLS, we pride ourselves on delivering premium quality meats.<\/p>"}},"question_3yTDJD":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"What is the best meat to buy?","text":"<p>With exotic meats available from far and wide, we have a huge range for you to choose from. The most premium of our meats are the Wagyu steaks. Looking for lamb? Why not try some of our New Zealand lamb cuts.<\/p>"}},"question_P66QVe":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Is lamb better than beef?","text":"<p>This is all down to personal preference. Lamb rends to be higher in calories, fats and cholesterol, whilst beef is rich in protein, iron and zinc.<\/p>"}},"question_MR9Rf7":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Can I buy meat online?","text":"<p>Absolutely! MLS delivers anywhere in Muscat in 2 Hours.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["question_aHXDb7","question_8gzLgT","question_JjTrRU","question_3yTDJD","question_P66QVe","question_MR9Rf7"],"settings":{"heading":"FAQs","heading_align":"text-center","color_scheme":"none","full_width":true}},"177589973903f7d808":{"type":"_blocks","blocks":{"ai_gen_block_11e2b50_H7iV3z":{"type":"ai_gen_block_11e2b50","settings":{"section_title":"MLS Gourmet Butchery","section_title_size":36,"store_title":"MLS Gourmet Butchery - Abu Dhabi","store_subtitle":"Meat Market, Mushrif Mall, Abu Dhabi","store_address":"Mushrif Mall, Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates","stor